---
// Component Imports
import ConfettiButton from '../components/ConfettiButton.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/main.astro';
import Canvas from '../components/Canvas.astro';
---

<Layout title="1228247">
<script id="worker" is:inline src="/utils/workerCanvas.js"></script>

    <div class="w-full flex flex-col bg-black">
        <div class="bg-black h-screen w-full flex justify-center">
            <div class="md:m-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-violet-500 rounded-lg w-full flex flex-col">
                <Canvas image="/images/black.jpg" messagePipe="2" width=320 height=320>
                    <div class="bg-transparent flex flex-shrink flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                            <ConfettiButton css="py-2 px-4" wrapperClass="opacity-0 md:mb-5 md:ml-5 md:mt-5">?</ConfettiButton>
                            <ConfettiButton 
                            css="w-full md:w-auto text-green-500 md:text-white text-2xl md:text-lg bg-black md:bg-transparent hover:bg-purple-700 py-2 px-4" 
                            link='https://explorer.solana.com/' 
                            wrapperClass="w-full md:w-auto md:ml-auto md:mr-5 md:mt-5">Block Explorer</ConfettiButton>
                            <ConfettiButton 
                            css="w-full md:w-auto text-purple-500 md:text-white text-2xl md:text-lg bg-black md:bg-transparent hover:bg-purple-700 py-2 px-4" 
                            link='https://phantom.app/download' 
                            wrapperClass="w-full md:w-auto md:mr-5 md:mt-5">download Phantom</ConfettiButton>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-transparent w-full flex-shrink md:flex-grow flex-row">
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-transparent w-full flex flex-grow flex-row items-center justify-center">
                        <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl font-bold bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-violet-500">Virtual NzD</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-transparent w-full flex flex-shrink flex-row items-center justify-center">
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-transparent w-full flex flex-shrink flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center">
                            <ConfettiButton 
                            link='https://solana.com/docs' 
                            css="w-full md:w-auto hover:bg-purple-700 bg-black py-6 px-10 text-2xl" 
                            wrapperClass="w-full md:w-auto md:m-3 md:pb-8">Documentation</ConfettiButton>
                            <ConfettiButton 
                            css="w-full md:w-auto bg-gradient-to-b hover:bg-gradient-to-t from-green-500 to-violet-500 py-6 px-24 text-4xl"
                            wrapperClass="w-full md:w-auto">Buy</ConfettiButton>
                            <ConfettiButton 
                            link='https://solana.com/' 
                            css="w-full md:w-auto hover:bg-purple-700 bg-black py-6 px-10 text-2xl" 
                            wrapperClass="w-full md:w-auto md:m-3 md:pb-8">Solana.com</ConfettiButton>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-transparent w-full flex-shrink md:flex-grow flex-row">
                    </div>
                </Canvas>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-transparent w-full flex justify-center">
            <div class="bg-transparent justify-center w-full items-center flex grow flex-col">
                <div class="m-5 border-2 border-zinc-200 justify-center 2xl:w-1/3 w-full items-center flex flex-grow flex-col rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="m-5 text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-200">Why this exists</h3>
                    <p class="m-5 text-lg text-justify text-zinc-200">
                    Are you a paranoid schizophrenic? Have you already declared
                    yourself a sovereign citizen and buried gold bars in your back yard?
                    Me too baby, me too. But sometimes I feel like I want a bank account 
                    that isn't at any risk of collapse. 
                    <br/><br/>
                    For most of my daily needs I use 
                    cash, I rarely use my bank account. But sometimes I want to be able to 
                    deposit my paycheck into an account without participating in the fractional 
                    reserve banking system that has been destroying our economy. That's why 
                    virtual nzd exists, deposit cash or pay with a credit card and hold your 
                    own virtual dollars in a decentralized banking system denominated in 
                    new zealand dollars. This is not a stable coin, it is an asymmetric asset
                    with a floating exchange rate. 
                    <br/><br/>
                    Use decentralized exchanges to convert between
                    virtual nzd and anything from Bitcoin to USDT, the echange rate on these exchanges 
                    is set automatically by the supply and demand curves for each currency, and in some cases 
                    you may be able to get a better deal buying through an exchange compared to buying through 
                    this payment gateway. We will always charge exactly $1 for 1 nzd. We only provide a fiat
                    on-ramp, we DO NOT provide any method of cashing back out of nzd into either cash or bank deposits, 
                    the virtual nzd is not intended to be a separate asset class to physical cash. As such 
                    we do not try to peg the cash out exchange rate to $1, and discourage holding this asset 
                    in the hopes of making money via speculation. 
                    <br/><br/>
                    If you do need to cash out you can use any centralized
                    exchange that offers nzd deposits, or via an over-the-counter transactions with a private buyer.
                    <br/><br/>
                    The long term goal of this asset class is to kill the Australian banks suckling on our economy.
                    <br/><br/>
                    Fuck those ozzy cunts.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

